            <h3>üí° Remember:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Present subjunctive forms:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>-ar verbs: change -ar to -e (hablar ‚Üí hable)</li>
                        <li>-er/-ir verbs: change to -a (comer ‚Üí coma, vivir ‚Üí viva)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Structure: Ojal√°/Espero que + (no) + [verb in present subjunctive]</li>
                <li>"Ojal√°" comes from Arabic and expresses a strong wish or hope</li>
                <li>Watch out for stem-changing verbs! They usually change in subjunctive too</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

